{
  "description": "A nighttime long exposure photograph showcases a vibrant city skyline with a prominent bridge illuminated in white and connecting to a cityscape filled with buildings. In the background, fireworks explode in a burst of color, adding to the dynamic nature of the scene. The city buildings are lit with a multitude of lights, creating a glittering effect. The bridge appears as a graceful curve and is adorned with bright white lights along its length. A darker area suggests a hillside or park in the middle ground. The water below reflects some of the city lights, creating shimmering trails. The overall composition emphasizes the grandeur of the city and the celebratory atmosphere created by the fireworks.",
